source.name: Records Control Schedules Portal
source.description: The Records Control Schedules (RCS) repository provides access to scanned versions of records schedules, or Standard Form 115, Request for Records Disposition Authority, that have been developed by Federal agencies and approved by the Archivist of the United States.
